node.text:
[#TheHedgehogAtHome] Everyone's trying to adjust to life during these unprecedented times, so it's always extra comforting to eat something that reminds us of how our "previous" days used to be.
.
Here's my chilled Signature Mango Jelly Smoothie (U.P. S$6.95) from @HuiLauShanSingapore at @Nex.Singapore. My all-time favourite dessert drink from Hong Kong. Something I always had on my family trips there when I was young. ❤️ I like slurping the jelly up, and the mango smoothie is blended on the spot using fresh mangoes.
.
With the recent developments in HK, I just hope that one day it will revert to be the same food and shopping paradise we know it to be. 🙏
.
PS: All takeaways at Hui Lau Shan Singapore are currently at 15% off! Swipe ⬅️ for more info.
.
.
.
.

@erikas_food_acc Thank you Erika! You gotta try it. I love all things mango! 😃
@makanwarrior Cant wait to go back to HK and just enjoy shopping and eating freely!
@yiulinglie Yes! Freshly cut and blended on the spot
@tuoi18 Thank you Tuoi, i am sure you will love this too 😆
